snippet.title: Arcade ZX Collection: TETRIS
snippet.description:
This is my 2nd game for the Zx Spectrum 48K, totally homebrew, using for programming Notepad+ in pure assembler
Now you can purchase it : 4€ digital version, 10€ tape version
Email me: bubu.marcianito@gmail.com

Or purchase it at bubu-marcianito.itch.io
